        <div class="steps">
            <h2 class="section-title"> 🍟Steps</h2>
            <ol>
                <li>Chop down the potato into slices.</li>
                <li>Firstly,fry the slices lighter in oil </li>
                <li> then freeze it for about 15 mins</li>
                <li>Now deep fry the slices</li>
                <li> Add pinch of salt and peri peri masala to it.</li>
                <li>Serve with sauce, mayannnaise, or your favorite toppings!</li>
            </ol>
